parameters:
Priestess Sophia: Is it true that Prince Rex is going to
turn Myukos into a sea of fire, as Corus-san said...?

Clea: Indeed, during the meeting, the Guild Master seemed
to consider it as a negotiation tactic.

Clea: It was a shocking statement, but if I think calmly, I
also feel the same way.

Priestess Sophia: That's right... Prince Rex, who is so
kind... doing something like that...

Priestess Sophia: I believe that someone like me, who would
not resort to the methods of the Imperial Dark Faction,
would never become a mad king...
Mage Relm: E-Everyone! Please come over here!
Clea: ...Are these the members of the organization?
Priestess Sophia: I will perform healing immediately!

Thief Nora: I-I don't think it's worth it. There's no sound
or scent of someone being alive...
Mage Relm: D-Did Celis-san do this...?

Clea: I don't think so. I would never do something like
tearing someone apart.

Clea: Let's search the abandoned graveyard. There might be
something wrong with Celis-san.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
